The abandoned one.

1044
01:11:14,338 --> 01:11:16,005
Do you remember?

1045
01:11:16,039 --> 01:11:17,173
Mnh-mnh.

1046
01:11:19,076 --> 01:11:21,610
There's a little girl
from far away

1047
01:11:21,644 --> 01:11:23,812
