1185
01:20:51,564 --> 01:20:53,933
Mom!

1186
01:20:53,967 --> 01:20:55,501
Aah! Lincoln!

1187
01:20:55,535 --> 01:20:57,803
Okay! Oh!

1188
01:20:57,838 --> 01:21:01,707
I couldn't breathe.
I thought I was...

